Symbol.Script_1D:
! iScaleDependentIDShow SHOWMODE_OFF = 0 SHOWMODE_MVO = 1 SHOWMODE_ON = 2
! iPatternStartDisplayed SHOW_PATTERN_NO = 0 SHOW_PATTERN_3D = 1 SHOW_PATTERN_ALWAYS = 2
Symbol.Script_UI:
stDialogTitle = `LIMA Settings`
totalWidth = 600 totalHeight = 100
offsetTop = 2 offsetBottom = 2 offsetLeft = 10 offsetRight = 10
outFldWdt1 = totalWidth / 2 - offsetLeft - offsetRight outFldWdt2 = outFldWdt1 / 2 - 1 outFldWdt3 = outFldWdt1 / 3 - 1 outFldWdt4 = 2 * outFldWdt3 + 2
hOutField = 15 hInField = 19 hOffsetRow = 5
yDiff = hOutField + hOffsetRow
xPosMiddle = totalWidth / 2 xPos1 = offsetLeft xPos2 = xPos1 + 250 + 10 xPos3 = xPos2 + 1 + 10
yCurr = offsetTop
! ============================================================================== ! UI Dialog ! ==============================================================================
ui_dialog stDialogTitle, totalWidth, totalHeight
xSize = 200
ui_outfield `Show Door/Window IDs Depending on Scale`, xPos1, yCurr, 250, hOutField yCurr = yCurr + yDiff
UI_RADIOBUTTON "iScaleDependentIDShow", SHOWMODE_OFF, `Always off`, xPos1, yCurr, xSize, hInField yCurr = yCurr + yDiff
UI_RADIOBUTTON "iScaleDependentIDShow", SHOWMODE_MVO, `Scale dependent`, xPos1, yCurr, xSize, hInField yCurr = yCurr + yDiff
UI_RADIOBUTTON "iScaleDependentIDShow", SHOWMODE_ON, `Always on`, xPos1, yCurr, xSize, hInField yCurr = yCurr + yDiff
! ============================================================================== UI_SEPARATOR xPos2, offsetTop, 1, yCurr-offsetTop ! ==============================================================================
yCurr = offsetTop
ui_outfield `Show Pattern Start Symbol`, xPos3, yCurr, 250, hOutField yCurr = yCurr + yDiff
UI_RADIOBUTTON "iPatternStartDisplayed", SHOW_PATTERN_NO, `Always off`, xPos3, yCurr, xSize, hInField yCurr = yCurr + yDiff
UI_RADIOBUTTON "iPatternStartDisplayed", SHOW_PATTERN_3D, `Only in 3D`, xPos3, yCurr, xSize, hInField yCurr = yCurr + yDiff
UI_RADIOBUTTON "iPatternStartDisplayed", SHOW_PATTERN_ALWAYS, `Always on`, xPos3, yCurr, xSize, hInField yCurr = yCurr + yDiff
